diff --git a/src/go.mod b/src/go.mod
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..8bf30e8
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/go.mod
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+module hello
+
+go 1.19
diff --git a/src/hello_world.go b/src/hello_world.go
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..50cfb13
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/hello_world.go
@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@
+package main
+
+import "fmt"
+
+func main() {
+    fmt.Println("Hello World")
+}
\ No newline at end of file
diff --git a/src/hello_world_test.go b/src/hello_world_test.go
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..ec551e9
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/hello_world_test.go
@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@
+package main
+
+import (
+    "testing"
+    "bytes"
+    "os"
+)
+
+func TestHelloWorld(t *testing.T) {
+    // Capture the output of the main function
+    old := os.Stdout
+    r, w, _ := os.Pipe()
+    os.Stdout = w
+
+    main()
+
+    w.Close()
+    var buf bytes.Buffer
+    buf.ReadFrom(r)
+    os.Stdout = old
+
+    if got := buf.String(); got != "Hello World\n" {
+        t.Errorf("Expected 'Hello World', got '%s'", got)
+    }
+}
\ No newline at end of file
